---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Mantra Academy is a Maths and Science tuition academy in Indirapuram, Ghaziabad, founded by Gurpreet Shahpuri with over 15 years of teaching experience."
  path="/about"
>
  <section class="section about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our story</p>
      <h1>Built on one idea: understand it properly the first time.</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__lede">
        Mantra Academy started with a simple frustration: too many students
        keep pace with a syllabus without ever really understanding it. We
        built a tuition academy around the opposite approach: slow down
        where it matters, build the foundation properly, and let confidence
        follow understanding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream-warm">
    <div class="container about-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Our mission</h2>
        <p>
          To help Grade 7–10 students across CBSE and ICSE boards build real
          command over Maths and Science, not just exam-ready answers, but
          concepts that hold up over time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>How we teach</h2>
        <p>
          We don't rush through the syllabus. Every student is guided
          step-by-step, with concept clarity prioritized over speed, so
          improvement is steady and lasting rather than a last-minute scramble.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero__lede { font-size: var(--step-1); max-width: 65ch; }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
